ygData.subject: Re: New camp
ygData.msgSnippet: Head to Lake of Ill Omen if you have Kunark. You can solo there or group till about level 30 then head over to Frontier Mountains. The exp and loot is great.
ygData.messageBody:
Head to Lake of Ill Omen if you have Kunark. You
can solo there or group till about level 30 then head
over to Frontier Mountains. The exp and loot is great.
Make sure you are invis for the run from FV to LOIO
because the spiders are red and mean even to a lvl 31.
Get some maps so you can have an idea how to get to
LOIO and also where to hunt. South side of the lake is
usually not crowded, also near the FM zone is good
because if you get into trouble someone is usually there
to help or you can just zone. <br><br>Keban
Arrowsmith<br>31 Ranger <br>Grand Master Fletcher (202)<br>Brell
Serilis
